{"global_seq": 11224, "batch_seq": 24, "idiom_id": "idiom-11224", "text": "不念旧情", "pinyin": "bù niàn jiù qíng", "short_explanation": "指人原则性强，不记挂过去的情义。"}
{"global_seq": 11225, "batch_seq": 25, "idiom_id": "idiom-11225", "text": "不惜本钱", "pinyin": "bù xī běn qián", "short_explanation": "为了达到目的不吝惜所花费的代价。"}
{"global_seq": 11226, "batch_seq": 26, "idiom_id": "idiom-11226", "text": "不惜血本", "pinyin": "bù xī xuè běn", "short_explanation": "为了达到目的不吝惜所花费的代价。"}
{"global_seq": 11227, "batch_seq": 27, "idiom_id": "idiom-11227", "text": "不愤不启", "pinyin": "bù fèn bù qǐ", "short_explanation": "愤：心里想弄明白而还不明白。"}
