{"global_seq": 11233, "batch_seq": 33, "idiom_id": "idiom-11233", "text": "不拔之策", "pinyin": "bù bá zhī cè", "short_explanation": "不拔：牢固不可拔除，即不可动摇。"}
{"global_seq": 11234, "batch_seq": 34, "idiom_id": "idiom-11234", "text": "不拘形迹", "pinyin": "bù jū xíng jī", "short_explanation": "形容言谈举止无拘无束，自由自在。"}
